makes a bps patch with a transform file. 
usage:
> makepatch.exe [transform file] [output file] ([log file])

transform file syntax:
# comment 
inc foo.tf   (inserts given transform file)
sb addr mask (sets bits at addr using mask)
cb addr mask (clears bits at addr using mask) 
s8 addr val (set byte)
s16 addr val (set word) 
ss addr len val (write string) 
t names tags command  (tags = "tag1,tag2") (creates tf of single command)
tstart names tags 
    command/tf 
tfend  (create a transform with multiple commands or other transforms)
encrypt ... (for race roms, not implemented yet)